Sentencas: The application of Sn1-xMxP2O7 electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cells is limited due to its poor sintering abilities.
Titulo: Facile Synthesis and Enhanced Intermediate Temperature Electrical Properties of Novel Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)3 Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: In this study, a new Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)(3) composite electrolyte was facile synthesized and the structural and microstructural properties were characterized by XRD and SEM.
Titulo: Facile Synthesis and Enhanced Intermediate Temperature Electrical Properties of Novel Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)3 Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: These results exhibit that the Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)(3) composite can be obtained by Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7 in-situ reacted with inorganic melt salt.
Titulo: Facile Synthesis and Enhanced Intermediate Temperature Electrical Properties of Novel Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)3 Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The electrical properties were tested using impedance spectroscopy in the range of 300 similar to 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Facile Synthesis and Enhanced Intermediate Temperature Electrical Properties of Novel Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)3 Composite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The highest conductivity of Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)(3) achieved was 6.3 x10(-2) S.cm(-1) in a dry nitrogen atmosphere at 700 degrees C. A H-2/O-2 fuel cell with a dense Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)(3) electrolyte membrane was also constructed and achieved maximum power output densities of 47.2 mW.cm(-2) and 130.9 mW cm(-2) at 600 degrees C and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Facile Synthesis and Enhanced Intermediate Temperature Electrical Properties of Novel Sn0.9Mg0.1P2O7/KSn2(PO4)3 Composite Electrolyte
